        <p>
Vietnam in recent years has developed an impressive step, the image is built up friendly destinations, attractions. Number of international visitors to Vietnam are increasing. In 2000, Vietnam welcomed 2.1 million international passengers in 2008 was 4.2 million international passengers and in 2010, the number of tourists to Vietnam will surpass 5 million, far beyond the category Initial target is 4.2 million. With a growth rate of average annual passenger traffic of about 20%, Vietnam is increasingly asserted a destination on the world tourism map. The number of domestic tourists in 2010 also estimated at 28 million, income from tourism is about 96,000 billion, contributing about 5% of GDP, create jobs for 1.4 million workers.
</p>
<br />
<p>
From this practice, the team we want IT applications in the field of tourism to contribute to increasing tourism in Vietnam is a favorite around the world. Project "Tourism in Vietnam" is a system of websites and software running on mobile. When tourists come to Vietnam, with smartphones in hand, the visitors easily locate their coordinates by the GPS. If visitors have to install software "Tourism in Vietnam", then easily share your captured images on the Web via GPRS. Also, mobile software also provides many useful information about tourism such as: find a way, find an ATM, tourist sites near the current location, the specialty restaurants. With a website, from images provided from users and visitors are brought back to the user experience of travel through a very realistic picture. Website is like a social network for tourism. You travel, you share photos on the website. Your friends to watch, comment, share links, voting images. Besides the website there are other similar functions on mobile software (find your way, find an ATM) is also linked to many restaurants and hotels to provide information on the Web, allowing contact to order online .
</p>
